Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:20.56,2:45:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧        太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:25.50,2:45:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:30.57,2:45:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下下
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:32.57,2:45:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给我500    请
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:35.51,2:45:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷看
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:42.58,2:45:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:48.59,2:45:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小安的这个这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:52.59,2:45:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么害羞的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:56.60,2:45:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好讲的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:00.60,2:46:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋装吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:04.60,2:46:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面购物的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:07.54,2:46:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很会穿起来有变形感
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:10.61,2:46:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们店员会想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:15.55,2:46:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是胸部上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:18.62,2:46:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿不上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:23.56,2:46:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:28.49,2:46:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不可以打开给他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:32.50,2:46:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:36.50,2:46:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞吗?     当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:39.57,2:46:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边都要坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:43.58,2:46:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生的话   对
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:46.51,2:46:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生的话呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:53.59,2:46:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在电车里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:46:57.59,2:47:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:00.53,2:47:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要关门
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:04.53,2:47:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点夹住
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:08.53,2:47:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛吗?   差点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:13.61,2:47:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时希望是小一点的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:19.61,2:47:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的    谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:23.62,2:47:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下请继续努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:26.55,2:47:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的   谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:33.49,2:47:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JULIA辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:36.56,2:47:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:40.57,2:47:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起共演
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:43.50,2:47:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第2次
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:46.57,2:47:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?    对阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:49.51,2:47:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:51.51,2:47:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前人不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:56.58,2:47:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是第一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:02.59,2:48:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:05.53,2:48:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小安很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:08.59,2:48:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小安还好吗?   很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:13.53,2:48:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部也很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:18.60,2:48:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JULIA的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:20.61,2:48:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:26.61,2:48:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么期待的吗?:
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:31.55,2:48:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的胸部感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:38.49,2:48:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:41.56,2:48:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好处呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:45.57,2:48:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:50.50,2:48:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比较高
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:54.51,2:48:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是配上胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:48:58.51,2:49:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:02.52,2:49:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:12.53,2:49:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:15.60,2:49:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:20.53,2:49:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:24.54,2:49:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是害羞的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:30.54,2:49:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为胸部很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:34.55,2:49:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上衣服的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:38.55,2:49:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣有时候太小
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:43.62,2:49:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会慢慢往下移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:49.50,2:49:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:53.50,2:49:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候内衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:56.57,2:49:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:49:59.51,2:50:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在长大吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:04.58,2:50:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:08.58,2:50:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我靠近点看
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:10.58,2:50:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:13.52,2:50:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:20.59,2:50:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了    对阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:25.53,2:50:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会慢慢移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:34.61,2:50:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:38.61,2:50:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待继续长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:40.61,2:50:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会唷
